%% 1. シーケンス図：学習フロー
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Client
    participant Supabase
    participant TTS as Text-to-Speech API

    User->>Client: 学習開始
    Client->>Supabase: 認証チェック
    Supabase-->>Client: 認証OK
    
    loop 学習セッション
        Client->>Client: 問題選択
        Client->>TTS: 音声生成リクエスト
        TTS-->>Client: 音声データ
        Client->>User: 音声再生
        User->>Client: 回答入力
        Client->>Supabase: 学習記録保存
        Supabase-->>Client: 保存完了
        Client->>Client: 次の問題準備
    end

%% 2. ユースケース図
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Login
    Login --> Dashboard: ログイン成功
    Dashboard --> NewStudy: 新規学習
    Dashboard --> Review: 復習
    Dashboard --> MixedStudy: 混合学習
    Dashboard --> IncorrectList: 誤答確認
    NewStudy --> Answer
    Review --> Answer
    MixedStudy --> Answer
    Answer --> [*]: 学習終了

%% 3. クラス図
classDiagram
    class User {
        +String id
        +String email
        +login()
        +logout()
    }
    class StudySession {
        +String id
        +String userId
        +StudyMode mode
        +startSession()
        +endSession()
    }
    class StudyRecord {
        +String id
        +String userId
        +String sentenceId
        +Int result
        +DateTime nextReview
        +Boolean mastered
        +save()
    }
    class Sentence {
        +String id
        +String content
        +getAudio()
    }
    User "1" -- "*" StudySession
    User "1" -- "*" StudyRecord
    StudySession "1" -- "*" StudyRecord
    StudyRecord "*" -- "1" Sentence

%% 4. アクティビティ図
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> SelectMode
    SelectMode --> GetQuestion
    GetQuestion --> PlayAudio
    PlayAudio --> UserAnswer
    UserAnswer --> SaveRecord
    SaveRecord --> CheckContinue
    CheckContinue --> GetQuestion: 継続
    CheckContinue --> [*]: 終了

%% 5. 状態遷移図
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> New
    New --> InProgress: 開始
    InProgress --> Answered: 回答
    Answered --> Mastered: 完璧
    Answered --> Review: 要復習
    Review --> InProgress: 再学習
    Mastered --> [*]

%% 6. ER図
erDiagram
    Users ||--o{ StudyRecords : "creates"
    StudyRecords }o--|| Sentences : "references"
    
    Users {
        uuid id PK
        string email
        timestamp created_at
    }
    StudyRecords {
        uuid id PK
        uuid user_id FK
        string sentence_id FK
        integer result
        timestamp next_review
        boolean mastered
        timestamp created_at
    }
    Sentences {
        string id PK
        string content
    }

